    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174300/extras/bc9da91e5b232f1908bdca72187b73d3.avif?t=1768886594\" width=616 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you like logic-puzzles? <i>Of course you do</i>, what a silly question! Piczle World of Puzzles brings together all your favourite Piczle puzzles in one addictive package!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From classic nonograms to colour logic-puzzles, from challenging brain-scratchers to relaxing mind-calmers, Piczle World of Puzzles is packed <i>to the hilt</i>, the <i>hilt </i>I say,  with picture-based logic-puzzles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Piczle Cross</strong> are classic nonograms. <strong>Piczle Color Cross</strong> are colour nonograms. <strong>Piczle Colors</strong> <i>(Currently under construction)</i> are a brain-bending variation on regular nonograms. <strong>Piczle Lines</strong> offers relaxing pixel-art based puzzling. And…more?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174300/extras/e004c340d898c10f293fff464d4bbce6.poster.avif?t=1768886594\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174300/extras/e004c340d898c10f293fff464d4bbce6.webm?t=1768886594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174300/extras/e004c340d898c10f293fff464d4bbce6.mp4?t=1768886594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174300/extras/28eb36870682c8e8fcddab75a38ba2a6.avif?t=1768886594\" width=616 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At Piczle Academy you won’t just learn how each logic-puzzle works or how to use the many, many gameplay options and tools at your disposal, it will also make you better at puzzling! Learn advanced techniques and challenge yourself with a series of brain-bending logic quizzes to hone your skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174300/extras/2c139bafd80d7966855aac86bf45615d.avif?t=1768886594\" width=616 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no wrong way to play. At Piczle Academy you learn about all the different ways to enjoy the puzzles on your own terms. Whether you are a seasoned logic-puzzler or a curious beginner, Piczle World of Puzzles is for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174300/extras/9e74a148317fad1a980b3bccb7cb7a7b.avif?t=1768886594\" width=616 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create, test and share your own puzzles with the Piczle community. Or play puzzles created by other Piczle players! Use intuitive editors and get feedback on your creations to put together </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174300/extras/3ee50c5cc1ea38af606e9d687688187b.avif?t=1768886594\" width=616 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174300/extras/1ea7244a063045844c245da3920188d2.avif?t=1768886594\" width=616 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Piczle World of Puzzles is free to start and offers copious amounts of free content. Daily puzzles, seasonal puzzle packs, a drip-feed of free puzzles will keep you occupied without spending a penny! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174300/extras/42e67075a98aa3ae556fb11c5cbb955f.avif?t=1768886594\" width=616 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For players who wish to support Score Studios, or for those hungry for even more there are DLC packages for each specific puzzle type to get more of the content you want, as well as some extras like profile stickers and puzzle themes!</p>",
